				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Where a histopathological characterisation of the cellular composition and disease condition of the sample was not performed under 6.3, and is needed, it shall be performed at this stage to assess the cellular composition and disease condition.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="40" splitType="Prevent">
