				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[6.7.2. General information for DNA isolation procedures:]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="70" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="70" uuid="622f9f83-2c98-4771-bbaa-79ba3ec47222"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Archived tissue blocks were trimmed before taking sections for DNA isolation, and this was documented
<br><font color="#004280">should</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="22" height="15" uuid="756f56da-5611-4711-bb04-bbd785c71f7d"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="a8ac2af1-db1f-414e-9dd2-3e151b51cc1e"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="d1661f7f-75b9-42f4-ad47-9b3f7da473b7">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffpe_dna_083_v2_a_v2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="17" height="15" uuid="cf1eeeb3-4bf8-4598-af60-9f7a3c5b6f99"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="8df9f68e-23d5-4268-a545-2247256192bd"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="72f34e5b-2e1f-4e45-b9a3-e18853cdcd34">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffpe_dna_083_v2_a_v2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("No")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="105">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="105" uuid="9d9e2b6a-9d6d-4d4c-a38c-7905d35468a2"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Formalin fixation introduces covalent modifications to DNA by addition of mono-methylol groups. In next steps electrophilic addition of N-methylol on an amino base leads to the formation of methylene bridges between two amino groups. Prolonged fixation leads to cross linking between DNA and proteins. Formaldehyde causes chemical modifications interfering with enzymatic downstream analysis such as PCR efficiency.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="85" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="85" uuid="2b094b00-0b22-4be5-b5be-65eda7605450"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[1. Did you use FFPE tissue with a fixation duration of 12-24 hrs for 5mm pieces in standard buffered formalin solution for DNA isolation?
<br><font color="#004280">should</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="22" height="15" uuid="67235390-e7e7-4266-8077-85f2b9234695"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="f99f4bcd-c797-4981-a945-0ae3a7ebdcec"/>
