				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="55" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="55" uuid="00d1b749-98c0-43c9-97b8-12a01d817fd6"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[4. DNA isolation performance was tested in a DNA proficiency test programme
<br><font color="#004280">should</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="22" height="15" uuid="604e0a4a-0db5-4333-9bdc-6793df90147c"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="6dff63fb-9d80-4383-8cde-871812a56ef7"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="525f93c4-1232-4a78-b0f4-297b426566b9">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffpe_dna_087_v2_v2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="17" height="15" uuid="026ed501-62ed-4076-8abb-e836e054c98f"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="aa098dd6-6a5e-45e4-994b-16de5db54866"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="e5a1ae47-99b3-4e06-8f49-1e3769bc9884">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffpe_dna_087_v2_v2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("No")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="60">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="60" uuid="520751c0-11c2-419e-8f7b-21214cc50b02"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[For all DNA isolation procedures, measures have to be included to reverse as much of the formaldehyde modifications as possible without further DNA degradation.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="130" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="130" uuid="ccdc2e19-1288-4fc3-afe6-bfcae222f912"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[a) Digestion with protein K and heating partially reverses introduced modifications of nucleic acids and protein-DNA crosslinks. Long incubation times at high temperatures may result in more fragmented DNA.
<br>
<br>Have you considered this method in your collection?]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="22" height="15" uuid="5b30759d-5981-4ecb-96e7-5afe8cd35f6a"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="86d165a7-b33d-4605-bc80-8bf69ce3343d"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="4f8e3ba7-0123-4080-82d8-4995a896461e">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{text5_2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="17" height="15" uuid="258ce9ec-d176-4e54-bda5-41b10494830e"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="8fcd5dee-f482-4b50-9a0e-225983ec5693"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="10" uuid="81787c44-d7de-4e7a-9c13-745470a933bc">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{text5_2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("No")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="115" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="115" uuid="0a29046e-aeed-47d0-8299-c36c672347cf"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[b) Alteration of DNA in FFPE tissues includes base modifications and deamination, which upon PCR or primer extension may lead to erroneous read-out.
<br>
<br>Have you considered this method in your collection?]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="22" height="15" uuid="a92e684e-7aab-40fc-8bcc-0b6848ed083b"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="3007ab67-7da8-4f95-8ab6-cbcdd4bf11f4"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="10" uuid="44ab45d4-aec5-4d59-8a0e-fda8a2e8fd6e">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{text6_2}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="17" height="15" uuid="7ed6acb9-200f-4927-a432-0c9ef640d2ee"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
