				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[4. Optional: Incubation with Rnase A was performed, in case RNA-free genomic DNA is required
<br> <font color="#004280">should</font>]]></text>
